# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001170> (active ecosystem management process)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "https://www.iucn.org/theme/protected-areas/about/protected-areas-categories/category-iv-habitatspecies-management-area") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001170> "A process during which an ecosystem, its parts, or the processes it participates in are modified by human intervention to accomplish an objective.")
